data.description: Situated on a generous corner lot, this three-bedroom, two-full bathroom home offers so much potential. Inside you will find a spacious and inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The bedrooms are designed with your comfort in mind, providing ample amounts of closet space. For car enthusiasts or those in need of extra storage, the oversized 2-car garage is a standout feature, conveniently connected to the home with a breezeway. Additionally, the property offers RV parking, ensuring space for your recreational vehicles. Enjoy the convenience of being close to shopping and town amenities. Whether you're running errands or exploring local attractions. Showings are by appointment only, please schedule yours today!
